{"id": "1413816751182843995", "channel_id": "1357183866183618741", "type": 19, "author_id": "152579843379167232", "author_name": ".somefish.", "author_bot": false, "content": "as a further explanation, It’s an oh for OverExalt. OE. not zero e. \n\nduplications go \ne0\nE1\nE2\nE3\n+1 (e4)\n+2\n+3\noe (overexalt, +4, e7)\n+5 \n…\n+12 (e15, for a total of sixteen copies )", "timestamp": "2025-09-06T09:23:00.927000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-06T09:24:29.365000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1385988420089675810"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1413739061579091979", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1357183866183618741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Flares' Comprehensive Beginner Guide to Morimens", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704"]}
{"id": "1413908156957986990", "channel_id": "1357183866183618741", "type": 0, "author_id": "220087061154234368", "author_name": "phallion", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm fairly new, but I found myself with an E3 Tulu and E2 Hameln. I like them both a lot, so I put together this team that looks a lot like Kai's end game team in the Start + End Game Team Comps tab.\n_ _\nIt's been fine facerolling for a bit, and overall fun to play out of everything I've tried, but I'm starting to hit a wall. \n_ _\nThere are a lot of options in terms of who to Rouse first, what to dupe w/ Ham, which exalt to battery, etc.\n_ _\n**What exactly is the win con for this comp from the guide, and what's generally the best way to get there?**", "timestamp": "2025-09-06T15:26:13.762000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1413908156681027604", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 2215760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1357183866183618741/1413908156681027604/image.png?ex=69cc9055&is=69cb3ed5&hm=7725da225a2a597e8be0fc89b2641b7a7a57467f862ee23fd81221a4757e17fa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1357183866183618741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Flares' Comprehensive Beginner Guide to Morimens", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704"]}
